				<article class="space-y-4 animate">
					<h5
						class="font-semibold animate text-black dark:text-white"
					>
						Profile
					</h5>
					<p class="animate">
						Intamately curious person. Passionate about the
						entanglement between humans and technology, and the ways
						we interact with the world.
					</p>
					<p>
